61400_xlarge.png?m=1657768109", "created": 1636525139, "last_modified": 1657768109}, "last_reply_by": "HalcyonTime", "last_touched": 1658501883, "title": "换了新手机后，眼睛老是感觉疲劳， OLED 屏幕到底伤不伤眼睛？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/867973", "created": 1658464917, "deleted": 0, "content": "以前用 LCD ，也没什么感觉。\r\n\r\n最近换了 OLED 国产屏幕，发现看久比较容易视觉疲劳。查了一下网上的评价，大部分都说 OLED 低亮度屏刷新伤眼。\r\n\r\n可问题现在新手机好多都是 OLED 屏幕，也没得选。都吹 OLED 各种省电各种颜色好，看着商家广告词，陷入了深深的沉思。", "content_rendered": "以前用 LCD ，也没什么感觉。<br /><br />最近换了 OLED 国产屏幕，发现看久比较容易视觉疲劳。查了一下网上的评价，大部分都说 OLED 低亮度屏刷新伤眼。<br /><br />可问题现在新手机好多都是 OLED 屏幕，也没得选。都吹 OLED 各种省电各种颜色好，看着商家广告词，陷入了深深的沉思。", "last_modified": 1658464917, "replies": 37, "id": 867973}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1656605007", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1656605007", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49927, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007", "stars": 7909, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 568870, "username": "qiubangzhu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/qiubangzhu", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b5a5ef9c0a0eb1e630db25e096693129?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b5a5ef9c0a0eb1e630db25e096693129?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b5a5ef9c0a0eb1e630db25e096693129?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1642049737, "last_modified": 1650468928}, "last_reply_by": "FreshOldMan", "last_touched": 1658549798, "title": "很久没更新支付宝，今天更新了一下，竟然成短视频 App 了？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868119", "created": 1658500195, "deleted": 0, "content": "真